If you want to make a change you have to start where you stand. The Cultural Enrighment Center offers a space for black youth in Fort Collins, CO to explore their identity and find their voice. If, like us, you believe in the work @cec_foco is doing, become a monthly donor at www.fococec.org/donate.

Kindling was brewed to give back 1% of revenue to our nonprofit partners, like @cec_foco, who create positive impact and lasting change.

node.text:
Double Pilsner is back for a special small batch, taproom release! This limited 4-pack is available at all three taprooms on Friday, August 20th. Head to the Fort Collins Taproom, @odellbrewingsloans, or @odellbrewingfivepoints to grab your 4pack - they'll likely go fast!⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Refreshing and delicate yet bold and assertive, the Double Pilsner's golden straw color leaves nowhere for imperfections to hide. Scents of pilsner malt and light floral hop aromas combine with a rich malt flavor to create a balanced and warming Imperial Pilsner.⁠

node.text:
A few years ago, we set out to create the haziest and juiciest IPA there had ever been. So we took to our Denver and Fort Collins pilot systems to start experimenting with the hypothesis that would lead to Pulp Theory. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
We used our hammer mill to fresh grind whole flower Galaxy hops to capture the most intricate essential oils, providing intense passionfruit and tangerine cream hop aromas. We might have gone a little mad but with a little #science, we created Pulp Theory. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Want to experience the madness? Click the link in our bio to find some near you.⁠
